{"id":61107,"date":"2019-09-11T09:00:10","date_gmt":"2019-09-10T23:00:10","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/?p=61107"},"modified":"2021-10-14T10:24:25","modified_gmt":"2021-10-14T00:24:25","slug":"migration-program-2018-19-visas-granted","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/migration-program-2018-19-visas-granted\/","title":{"rendered":"Migration Program 2018-19 \u2013 Visas Granted"},"content":{"rendered":"[vc_row type=&#8221;in_container&#8221; full_screen_row_position=&#8221;middle&#8221; column_margin=&#8221;default&#8221; column_direction=&#8221;default&#8221; column_direction_tablet=&#8221;default&#8221; column_direction_phone=&#8221;default&#8221; scene_position=&#8221;center&#8221; text_color=&#8221;dark&#8221; text_align=&#8221;left&#8221; row_border_radius=&#8221;none&#8221; row_border_radius_applies=&#8221;bg&#8221; overlay_strength=&#8221;0.3&#8243; gradient_direction=&#8221;left_to_right&#8221; shape_divider_position=&#8221;bottom&#8221; bg_image_animation=&#8221;none&#8221;][vc_column column_padding=&#8221;no-extra-padding&#8221; column_padding_tablet=&#8221;inherit&#8221; column_padding_phone=&#8221;inherit&#8221; column_padding_position=&#8221;all&#8221; column_element_spacing=&#8221;default&#8221; background_color_opacity=&#8221;1&#8243; background_hover_color_opacity=&#8221;1&#8243; column_shadow=&#8221;none&#8221; column_border_radius=&#8221;none&#8221; column_link_target=&#8221;_self&#8221; gradient_direction=&#8221;left_to_right&#8221; overlay_strength=&#8221;0.3&#8243; width=&#8221;1\/1&#8243; tablet_width_inherit=&#8221;default&#8221; tablet_text_alignment=&#8221;default&#8221; phone_text_alignment=&#8221;default&#8221; bg_image_animation=&#8221;none&#8221; border_type=&#8221;simple&#8221; column_border_width=&#8221;none&#8221; column_border_style=&#8221;solid&#8221;][vc_column_text]A total of <strong>160,323<\/strong> visas were granted for the 2018-19 Permanent Migration program. This represents <em><strong>the lowest number in a decade<\/strong><\/em><b> <\/b>as indicated by the Department of Immigration.<\/p>\n<p>The figures published by the Department reveal that <strong>109,713<\/strong> visas were granted under the Skilled Migration program and <strong>50,610<\/strong> visas were granted under the Family stream.<\/p>\n<p>With the Migration program capped at an <strong>annual rate of 160,000 per year<\/strong>, the government expects the number of permanent migrants to be even lower over the coming four years. The decision to maintain the intake at 160,000 came after a period of intense public debate about the size of Australia\u2019s population and effects of migration.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-61127\" src=\"https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/permanent-migration-2018-2019.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"378\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/permanent-migration-2018-2019.jpg 864w, https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/permanent-migration-2018-2019-300x189.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/permanent-migration-2018-2019-768x484.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2>Family Stream<\/h2>\n<p>Over 70% of the places in the Family stream were filled under the <strong>Partner program<\/strong> with a total of 39,918 visas granted.<\/p>\n<h2><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-61149 \" src=\"https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/family-stream.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"688\" height=\"436\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/family-stream.jpg 879w, https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/family-stream-300x190.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/family-stream-768x487.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 688px) 100vw, 688px\" \/>Skill Stream<\/h2>\n<p>The bulk of the places in the <strong>Skilled stream<\/strong> were filled by skilled workers under the Skilled Independent and Employer Nomination Scheme programs, with 34,247 and 33,025 visas granted respectively.<\/p>\n<p>Despite these low numbers, there is a 44 per cent increase in the number of places delivered under the <strong>Regional Sponsor Migration Scheme<\/strong>, compared to the previous program.\u00a0 This together with the recently announced new regional visas and the dedicated 23,000 places for regional skilled migrants, shows the Department\u2019s intention to focus on <strong>regional migration<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<p><strong><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-61150 \" src=\"https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/skill-stream.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"730\" height=\"527\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/skill-stream.jpg 971w, https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/skill-stream-300x217.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/skill-stream-768x554.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 730px) 100vw, 730px\" \/><\/strong><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3><strong>Source<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>Minister\u2019s Media release: <a href=\"https:\/\/minister.homeaffairs.gov.au\/davidcoleman\/Pages\/migration-program-focusing-regional-australia.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https:\/\/minister.homeaffairs.gov.au\/davidcoleman\/Pages\/migration-program-focusing-regional-australia.aspx<\/a><\/p>\n<p>Learn more about the Migration program planning levels: <a href=\"https:\/\/immi.homeaffairs.gov.au\/what-we-do\/migration-program-planning-levels\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https:\/\/immi.homeaffairs.gov.au\/what-we-do\/migration-program-planning-levels<\/a>[\/vc_column_text][divider line_type=&#8221;No Line&#8221; custom_